the Misses Danaidesdaughters of a king, my dear, and
eminent collaborators with Tantalus, in the liquid causedeep
in the science of water powerLadies, our new queen will
give out cards for a ball, as soon as she is rested from her
journey. Lord Sysiphus, my lovea great mineralogist.
Hippodamia, we must tax thy dutiful loyalty to set down that
water pitcher, and do us a few errands. Let our people hear
the news, and share their sovereign's joy. First see chief
justice
Minos, and desire him to hasten to the palace to draw a
