upon our heads, the memory of the happy days we had
labored
in her household was green and bitter in our hearts.
We had her best recommendation for sobriety, honesty, and
extensive capacity, in our pockets.
Optim spei juvenis
,
[9]
[9]
The common complimentary lie in the diploma.
was wreathed around our brows. We were proud, and
humbled
